<tal:w condition="context/@@annotator-enabled">
<div class="annotator-help-panel">
    <h2>Welcome to the Siyavula Annotator!</h2>
    <br/> <br/>
    <h3> Instructions: </h3>
    <ul>
        <li> Click and drag to highlight text.</li>
        <li> Click on the <img src="annotator-icon.png"
                               tal:attributes="src string:${context/@@plone_portal_state/portal_url}/++resource++emas.theme.resources/annotator-icon.png"
                               alt="Annotator button" height="5%" align="middle"/></li>
        <li> Enter your comment and choose the correct category.</li>
        <li> Click Save. </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>The colour codes: </h3>
    <p> The annotations are colour coded according to their categories:</p>
    <ul>
        <li> <span class="annotator-hl annotator-hl-errata">    Errata     </span>: Something is wrong with this text. </li>
        <li> <span class="annotator-hl annotator-hl-comment">   Comment    </span>: Any comments, critique etc.  </li>
        <li> <span class="annotator-hl annotator-hl-suggestion">Suggestion </span>: Suggest something! </li>
    </ul>
</div>
<a class="annotator-help-trigger" href="#">Help</a>
</tal:w>
